[node name="context-text" parent="Background/MarginContainer/right-side/Game info/MarginContainer/context-box" parent_id_path=PackedInt32Array(227325637) index="0" unique_id=531777206]
text = "The sun rises, it's rays of light beaming through the clear glass window hanging just above your bed. It's round, with no visible bars or decorations between - set within a white metallic wall. Your room is decorated fairly plainly, having only been adopted here a month ago by your new caretaker. Your head is too foggy to think much of it right now, so you pick yourself up from your bed and head towards the bathroom.

The doors open and shut automatically as you approach. Despite being made of well varnished wood, you can barely hear them open and shut on their magnetic tracks - leaving only your footsteps populating the wooden hallway and echoey bathroom as head on your way.

You disrobe sluggishly, getting a good look of yourself in the mirror...
Who are you?"
script = ExtResource("2_ea161")

